ğŸ§  Askinfinity AI Chatbot
Askinfinity is a web-based AI chatbot that offers users a seamless and intelligent conversational experience. Built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, and powered by the Gemini API, Askinfinity serves as a multi-mode assistant with specialized roles including General Chat, Coding Help, Philosophy Talk, and Helpdesk Support.

ğŸŒ Live Demo: www.askinfinity.xyz

