ğŸ’¾ Persistent Chat History: Chats are saved using localStorage, allowing users to revisit past conversations.

ğŸŒ“ Light/Dark Mode Toggle: UI includes theme switching with preference remembered across sessions.

ğŸ“ File Upload & Camera Capture: Users can upload .txt, .pdf, .docx files or capture photos directly from the webcam.

ğŸ’¬ Real-Time Typing Animation: AI responses appear with a dynamic typing animation for better UX.

ğŸ“± Responsive Design: Fully functional across all screen sizes â€” mobile, tablet, and desktop.

ğŸ§  Powered by Gemini AI: Utilizes Gemini API for powerful and context-aware responses.

ğŸ› ï¸ Technologies Used
Frontend: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (ES6)

AI Backend: Gemini API (via HTTP requests)

Hosting: Cloudflare Pages

Storage: localStorage for user preferences and chat history

Media Handling: HTML5 FileReader, Webcam Access via getUserMedia

